Text: RE Hello Cc Vince How are you this week My week is pretty relaxing I am taking the training for the very last product of my company called Voicenet and I will achieve the highest state of initiation with Destia Viatel products ha Unfortunatelly I have not been promoted for Business VIP Representative the position associated with T as I do not have any experience with it I am blaming myself because I cannot discipline myself to study consequently every day for GMAT All the best to you and see you on Saturday Patrycja Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday March PM To Subject Re Hello Hello Still in New York Leaving tomorrow night for Houston See you on Saturday I shall send you more detailed directions on Friday Take care Vince

RE Hello Cc I just received your message Are still in NYC I like it a lot I wish my job was associated with traveling According to Saturday meeting I will be there Have a save trip back home patrycja From Save Address Block Sender To Save Address CC Save Address Subject Re Hello Date Mon Mar EST Reply Reply All Forward Delete Previous Next Close Hello Patrycja Greetings from the Big Apple Saturday works for me Lets meet at pm at Carrabbas Its an Italian restaurant on I in the Woodlands After you pass Conroe take the Research Forest exit miles past Conroe and stay on the feeder road Go through the lights Research Forest intersection with I As you continue along the feeder road you will pass on your right the Woodlands Mall and the ExxonMobil building The restaurant will be on your right about yards before the next lights I and Sawdust I shall have my cell phone with me In case you arrive early you can stop at my home Snowbird Place I shall send you later the instructions how to get there I shall leave home around Look forward to meeting you Vince
